🧠 ⚡ 5 MARKS ANSWERS

1. Strategic Assessment
Strategic assessment me check kiya jata hai ki project company ke goals ke according hai ya nahi.
Agar project company ke future growth me help karta hai to wo accept hota hai.

Example:
AI company agar AI project banaye → correct
Website banaye → mismatch

2. Technical Assessment
Isme check hota hai ki project technically possible hai ya nahi.
Team ke skills, tools aur technology evaluate ki jati hai.

3. Cost Benefit Analysis
Isme cost aur benefit compare kiya jata hai.
Agar benefit cost se zyada hai to project profitable hai.

4. Cash Flow Forecasting
Future me paisa kab aayega aur kab jayega uska estimate banaya jata hai.
Isse financial planning easy hoti hai.

5. Risk Evaluation
Project ke risks identify aur analyze kiye jate hai.
Unka impact aur probability check ki jati hai.

6. Project Scheduling
Project ke tasks ko time ke according arrange karna.
Start aur end time define kiya jata hai.

7. Sequencing and Scheduling
Sequencing me tasks ka order decide hota hai.
Scheduling me timing decide hoti hai.

8. Network Planning Models
PERT aur CPM jaise models use karke project ka flow diagram banaya jata hai.

9. Forward & Backward Pass
Forward pass se earliest time nikalte hai.
Backward pass se latest time nikalte hai.

10. Activity Float
Float wo extra time hai jo delay ke liye available hota hai.

